621
01:18:07,099 --> 01:18:11,149
嘘 我当然知道你最后一定会发现的 好吗?
Shh. Of course I knew you were gonna find out eventually, OK?

622
01:18:11,312 --> 01:18:14,282
但是不要怪我不告诉你 你从来也不想知道这些
But don't blame me for not telling you. You never wanted to know.

623
01:18:14,440 --> 01:18:15,908
你别把这一切都试图推给我
Don't try and pin this on me.

624
01:18:16,066 --> 01:18:18,694
