- Just when I finish the book!  - This book isn't for us. It's for you.

674
01:20:36,957 --> 01:20:38,880
特蕾西 不要那样说 那并不是真的
Tracy, don't say that. That's not true.

675
01:20:39,043 --> 01:20:42,092
的确是这样 有很多方式去支撑这个家
It is true. There are plenty of other ways you can provide for this family.

676
01:20:42,296 --> 01:20:45,015
做什么呢? 教书?
Doing what? Teaching?

677
01:20:45,174 --> 01:20:47,723
编辑新闻教科书?
Editing journalism textbooks?

678
01:20:47,885 --> 01:20:54,439
你不明白吗 写作是我的人生意义所在?
Don't you understand that writing is what gives my life meaning?

679
01:20:54,600 --> 01:20:57,820
这些书是我宝贵的遗产
These books are my legacy.

680
01:21:01,065 --> 01:21:04,786
埃里森 我一直都支持你做自己热爱的事情
I have always supported you doing what you love, Ellison.

681
01:21:04,943 --> 01:21:07,696
但写作并非你人生意义所在
But writing isn't the meaning of your life.

682
01:21:08,739 --> 01:21:13,336
你和我 我们的婚姻才是你人生的意义所在
You and me, right here, this marriage' that's the meaning of your life.

683
01:21:13,535 --> 01:21:17,256
你的遗产则是艾希莉和特雷弗
And your legacy, that's Ashley and Trevor.

684
01:21:17,414 --> 01:21:20,133
你的孩子就是你宝贵的遗产
Your kids are your legacy.

685
01:21:33,097 --> 01:21:36,522
