Your daddy got Daddy in trouble.

687
01:21:38,936 --> 01:21:42,861
- 对不起 我不该在墙上画画的  - 我晓得了
- I'm sorry I painted on the wall.  - I know.

688
01:21:43,023 --> 01:21:45,117
做个好梦
You get a good night's sleep.

689
01:21:51,740 --> 01:21:55,790
这就是我为证明这事所写的书 对吧?
So here's the book I wrote proving it, right?

690
01:21:55,953 --> 01:21:56,954
的确是
Exactly.

691
01:21:57,121 --> 01:22:01,092
言归正传 你是不是想要组建家庭了? 这事在计划中吗?
Kidding aside, would you want a family? Is that in the cards?

692
01:22:01,250 --> 01:22:02,297
