697
01:22:16,473 --> 01:22:20,103
接着你会猜想"儿子会像我吗?女儿会像她妈妈吗?"
and then you wonder "Is he gonna look like me? Is she gonna look like her?"

698
01:22:20,310 --> 01:22:22,404
你在大脑中替她们粉刷房间 接着...
You paint rooms in your head and...

699
01:22:33,532 --> 01:22:35,205
该睡觉了
Time for bed.

700
